entries.femaleVariant: What the hell's got you so amused?
Ah, saw some funny-ass shit go down's all. Some juvees sportin' fake IDs tried to slink past all cool, 'n' like it was nobody's biz.
I told 'em to spin and delta, but they was tenacious... Made their way 'round back – bathroom window, popped in through that.
Guess they were itchy in heat…
I'd say so. Just… once they's inside, one of those kids bumped into his mama. She'd told the fam she worked at a hotel... Rough stuff, huh?
Rough's not the word. Try disaster, sad sich.
